Be careful though: If you enable this option, there is a chance that payments are made with the corresponding order being already canceled.

Attiva questa impostazione per annullare gli ordini in attesa del cliente quando torna alla pagina del carrello e di un prodotto non è più disponibile. Attenzione, però: se si attiva questa opzione, c'è una possibilità che i pagamenti vengano effettuati con l'ordine corrispondente che é già stato annullato.

* Required Fields: When the store is not available (network outage, server failure or any other outage), when the feedback of Concardis PayEngine 3.0 is sent, then the transaction state is not updated. Hence no order confirmation e-mail is sent and the order is not in the paid state. By activating the transaction update, such transactions can be authorized later over direct link. To use this feature the update service must be activated and the API username and the API password must be set.
* campo obbligatorio: When the store is not available (network outage, server failure or any other outage), when the feedback of Concardis PayEngine 3.0 is sent, then the transaction state is not updated. Hence no order confirmation e-mail is sent and the order is not in the paid state. By activating the transaction update, such transactions can be authorized later over direct link. To use this feature the update service must be activated and the API username and the API password must be set.
